\subsection{Phase 2: Semantic Segmentation and Vectorization}

The PyTorch U-Net mathematically differentiates raw edge-pixels into specific spatial concepts (Walls vs Void). This array is then translated into mathematical, machine-readable $(x,y)$ geometry using topological simplification.

